T02TD3625E:245a-1: badzra dzva la aa na l'arka s'a dha nam /
T02TD3625E:245a-3: rdo rje me dang nyi ma 'bar ba'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD3625E:245a-4: rdo rje me dang nyi ma 'bar ba la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3625E:245a-5: de nyid bzhin du stong pa nyid kyi rjes la nyi ma la h'um yig mthing ga yongs su gyur pa las /
T02TD3625E:245a-6: rdo rje me dang nyi ma 'bar ba sku mdog mthing ga 'bar ba'i phreng ba 'khrigs pa'i 'od can /
T02TD3625E:245a-12: snying rje'i nyams dang ldan pa'i zhabs bzhi pa /
T02TD3625E:245a-13: g-yas kyi phyag bzhis rdo rje dang /
T02TD3625E:245a-17: g-yon gyi phyag bzhis dril bu dang /
T02TD3625E:245a-20: kha tv'am ga ba dan sna tshogs pa dang bcas pa bsnams pa /
T02TD3625E:245a-21: dbu skra skya bo'i tshogs me 'bar ba can /
T02TD3625E:245a-22: shin tu 'jigs pa sbrul chen po 'khyil bas lag gdub dang /
T02TD3625E:245a-28: sgyu ma chen po'i 'khor lor byas pa bzhi la chung ma dang bcas pa'i khyab 'jug g-yas brkyang ba'i zhabs kyis mnan pa dbang du byed pa bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD3625E:245a-29: de nas phyag rgya bcing bar bya ste /
T02TD3625E:245a-30: lag mthil rdo rje bcings pa'i sor mo 'bar ba'i snying bo'i dbus su mthe bong gnyis blang bar bya'o //
T02TD3625E:245a-31: de nas sngags bzlas par bya ste /
T02TD3625E:245a-32: aom badzra dzva l'a na l'arka h'um zhes so //
T02TD3625E:245a-33: rdo rje me dang nyi ma 'bar ba'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so //
